&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;This role is about enabling the Development Teams towards an environment where continuous improvement is the norm and where everyone’s common goal is having fun delivering high quality valuable working software continuously.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
