&lt;li&gt;Helping cross-functional Team focus on creating valuable incremental outcome for the business that meet the Definition of Done.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work on increasing transparency around work and collaboration to help team identify and remove impediments by themselves.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Help the team be better at development practices to ease change.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Ensuring that all Scrum events take place, are productive and team can learn from it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
