&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Helping employees and stakeholders understand and enact an empirical approach for complex work.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
