&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Cloud Infra: Google Cloud, Kubernetes, Docker&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Devops: Gitlab, Terraform, Ansible, Sonarqube, Sonatype Nexus, Vault&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Datastore and Service Bus: Redis, Mongo, Kafka&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
