&lt;li&gt;Act as the voice of the customer while working deeply with risk, business, and engineers to ensure the product is customer-centric yet robust.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and refine the product backlog by synthesizing business growth targets with risk constraints and capital efficiency to ensure the product roadmap maximizes impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive the execution and successful delivery of the prioritized backlog, collaborating closely with engineering throughout the product lifecycle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure complete transparency and strategic alignment across all stakeholders by clearly communicating product strategy, business objectives, and project goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
