&lt;li&gt;Strong ability to foster a collaborative, accountable, and high-performing team environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thrives in a fast-moving environment with the ability to turn ambiguity into action.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
