&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Product Lead within our Digital Bank, you will play a pivotal role in &lt;strong&gt;empowering internal teams to serve customers effectively and efficiently&lt;/strong&gt;, while elevating the overall banking experience. You will own product outcomes for internal platforms, tools, and capabilities that enable customer service, operations, risk, and other internal teams to deliver seamless, high-quality customer experiences at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
