&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive product strategy by identifying opportunities, defining clear goals, and aligning initiatives with clan and company objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate business and customer needs into a clear product vision and roadmap, balancing short-term delivery with long-term impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion customer-centric design to ensure internal products enhance team effectiveness and the overall customer experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stakeholder Management &amp;amp; Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build trusted relationships across business, technology, operations, and leadership teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate complex organizational dynamics, proactively manage expectations, and balance competing priorities while maintaining product vision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate open communication, encourage diverse perspectives, and constructively resolve conflicts to drive alignment and progress.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Delivery &amp;amp; Execution&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead cross-functional teams to execute and deliver high-quality internal products efficiently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Align tasks with strategy, manage resources effectively, and adapt plans as priorities evolve.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data-Driven Decision Making&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Promote data-driven decision making by analyzing relevant data, identifying gaps, and validating assumptions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Balance deep analysis with rapid experiments to iterate quickly and inform prioritization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer-Centric Design&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure internal products are designed with the end customer in mind, improving both team efficiency and customer outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven product leadership experience, ideally within &lt;strong&gt;digital banking, fintech, or regulated environments&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of delivering &lt;strong&gt;internal platforms, tools, or enablement products&lt;/strong&gt; that improve efficiency and customer outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills and experience using data to guide product decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills with the ability to simplify complexity and align diverse teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to navigate organizational dynamics, build trust, and influence decisions at multiple levels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A customer-first mindset, understanding that &lt;strong&gt;great internal products lead to great customer experiences&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Join Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shape products that directly enable teams to serve customers better at scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Influence strategy, execution, and outcomes in a high-impact product leadership role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work in a mission-driven digital bank focused on innovation, trust, and customer experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

